<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>浅草</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="css/goods/goods.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="css/goods/goods_details.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="css/lease/leaseDetails.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="https://cdn.bootcss.com/html5shiv/3.7.3/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.bootcss.com/respond.js/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
</head>
<body>
<%include ../index/header.ejs%>
<section style="margin-top: 220px">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 goodsHeader">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
                        <span>首页</span>
                        <span>/</span>
                        <span>租赁</span>
                        <span>/</span>
                        <span>租赁详情</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mycontent">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-9">
                <div class="goodsDecImg">
                    <img src="../img/lease/T1.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                </div>
                <!--用户评论-->
                <div class="col-xs-12">
                    <div class="userComments">
                        <!--<a href="#" target="goodsBox">-->
                            <!--<span>商品详情</span>-->
                        <!--</a>-->
                        <a href="userComment.html" target="goodsBox">
                            <span>商品详情</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-3">
                <div class="goodsIntr">
                    <h1><%=lease_details[0].detailsName%></h1>
                    <div class="goodsLine"></div>
                    <h2>¥<%=lease_details[0].detailsPrice%></h2>
                    <div class="goodsNum">
                        <span>商品编号： <span><%=lease_details[0].goodsSn%></span></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="goodsClass">
                        <span>分类：<span class="allgoodsSpan"><%=lease_details[0].goods_desc%></span></span>
                    </div>
                    <button type="button" class="btn my_btn pull-left" id="addShop">加入购物车</button>
                    <div class="pull-left myinput">
                        <span class="pull-left" id="numRedu"></span>
                        <input type="number" value="1" class="pull-left" id="numValue">
                        <span class="pull-left" id="numadd"></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-offset-1">
        <p>星期租：星期租 = 押金（￥200）+ 植被培养费（￥300） + 其他费用（￥118）</p>
        <p>月月租：月月租 = 押金（￥200）+ 植被培养费（￥300） + 其他费用（￥118）* 优惠折扣（80%）</p>
        <p>年年租：年年租 = 押金（￥200）+ 植被培养费（￥300） + 其他费用（￥118）* 优惠折扣（60%）</p>
    </div>
    <div class="details">
        <%for (var i =0;i<lease_details.length;i++){%>
            <%if (i%2==0){%>
                <div class="productOne">
                    <div class="productText">
                        <p class="productTitle"><%=lease_details2[i*4].descText%></p>
                        <%if (i==0){%>
                        <p><%=lease_details2[i+1].descText%></p>
                        <p><%=lease_details2[i+2].descText%></p>
                        <p><%=lease_details2[i+3].descText%></p>
                        <%}else {%>
                        <p><%=lease_details2[i*2].descText%></p>
                        <p><%=lease_details2[i*3].descText%></p>
                        <p><%=lease_details2[i*4].descText%></p>
                        <%}%>
                    </div>
                    <div class="productImg">
                        <img src="<%=lease_details[i].goodsImg%>">
                    </div>
                </div>
            <%}else {%>
                <div class="productOne">
                    <div class="productText2">
                        <p class="productTitle2"><%=lease_details2[i*4].descText%></p>
                        <p><%=lease_details2[i*2].descText%></p>
                        <p><%=lease_details2[i*3].descText%></p>
                        <p><%=lease_details2[i*4].descText%></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="productImg2">
                        <img src="<%=lease_details[i].goodsImg%>">
                    </div>
                </div>
            <%}%>
        <%}%>
    </div>
</section>
<%include ../index/footer.ejs%>
<div class="myShopDiv" id="myShopDiv">
    <div class="myshopCart">购物车</div>
    <div class="myScorll" id="myScorll">
        <ul>
            <%for (var i=0;i<lease_details.length;i++) {%>
            <li>
                <img src="<%=lease_details[i].goodsImg%>" class="img-responsive pull-left">
                <span><%=lease_details[i].goods_type%>-</span>
                <span><%=lease_details[i].goodsName%></span>
                <span>x</span>
                <span><%=lease_details[i].goods_num%></span>
            </span>
                <span title="删除" class="pull-right mydelSpan">×</span>
            </li>
            <%}%>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center xjMoney">
        <span>小计¥<span></span></span>
    </div>
    <a href="/order">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-block btn_mysum">结算</button>
    </a>
</div>
<script src="js/lease/leaseDetails.js"></script>
<script src="js/jquery-3.3.1.js"></script>
<script src="js/bootstrap.js"></script>
<script src="js/goods/goods_details.js"></script>
<script src="js/goods/goods.js"></script>
</body>
</html>